Build: run ./build_jedi.sh
If compiled successfully, run with run_jedi.sh

For using Wiimote:
activate Wii during start-up of program.

Controls:
Space Bar: Activate/Deactivate sword
A : left
D : right
W : forward
S : backward

Known issues:
- Program crashes while terminating, due to some memory deallocation. This has something to do with bullet engine and couldn't be solved.
- Rendering for the rift decreases performance, which is why it is disabled by default, but can be set to true in "main.cc" 
